Title
Reducing the Environmental Costs of Frequent Rocket Launches in the Era of LEO Broadband Expansion

Research Question
In the context of rapid LEO satellite broadband expansion, to what extent can technological strategies such as reusable launch vehicles, alternative propellants, and satellite miniaturization reduce the environmental costs of frequent launches?

